      "content": "hey, i have this really bad lower back pain like its making it hard to sit down. i started taking 400mg ibuprofen but it wears off so fast. is it a good idea if i just take another 400mg every 2 hours so i dont have to deal with the pain coming back? i just want to stay ahead of it.",
